{"tid":846380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑幫男被嘲似「戇豆先生」而撻朵 今被判緩刑3年","createTime":"2018-10-03T11:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T11:48:36.000Z","uid":179810,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f639b408decf28352426c76275eed194736343a0","tid":846380,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538561373_d9cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538561373_d9cd.jpg&h=3a74ceeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n警方臥底探員2015年滲入黑幫「和勝和」調查，成功與幫內兄弟混熟。眾人前年3月深夜在上水清河邨內流連兼吹水，其中一名兄弟因被嘲笑似「戇豆先生」而情緒激動，反駁：「<span style=\"color: red;\">X你咪X再講，陣間傳到出去俾我大佬臘爺知，我仲洗喺上水玩？實俾我勝和兄弟笑。</span> 」「戇豆男」今在粉嶺裁判法院承認聲稱是三合會社團成員一罪，判監8個月緩刑3年。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告許嘉誠（29歲）現任地盤工，有穩定工作，承諾不會再犯。<br />\n<br />\n臥底探員2015年5月滲入和勝和潛伏1年，案發於2016年3月7日深夜11時許，臥底、被告以及另外9人在清河邨閒聊，期間外號「奶茶」的男子嘲笑被告酷似「戇豆先生」，被告聞言激動要求「奶茶」閉嘴，否則傳出去會遭勝和兄弟恥笑。警方5個月後拘捕被告，他警誡下否認指控。<br />\n<br />\n成件事幾好笑<br />\n臥底咗一年就為咗捉人自稱三合會"},{"pid":"7c2b8a52c6151a8fe57aeca33c14fda5d25fdda8","tid":846380,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3a3f6d8ca79332ba345e037fa1dc5ac01c5f72","tid":846380,"uid":174115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"叫就嘉誠都係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08279b23551ff5b7f308a2aaa362075f1779fc7e","tid":846380,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:23:04.000Z","msg":"想睇下有幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf5aea4cc32135db2fad75f48388f35b4e8035e","tid":846380,"uid":41315,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"「戇豆男」今在粉嶺裁判法院<span style=\"color: red;\">承認聲稱是三合會社團成員一罪</span>，判監8個月緩刑3年。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指被告許嘉誠（29歲）現任地盤工，有穩定工作，承諾<span style=\"color: red;\">不會再犯。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不會再犯<br />\n即係不會再聲稱係三合會成員 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fa8bae1ea0db72efcea4e68bd2790d64ced701","tid":846380,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"奶荼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇咖啡?"},{"pid":"65e4caa32558a01e8d1addca7695e8213b281520","tid":846380,"uid":71166,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"屌 個卧底好賤呀 捉呢啲「自稱三合會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然唔係捉藏毒 打鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7411b674c805ccb623de692712c44c65cf00100d","tid":846380,"uid":40478,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"咁佢自爆左身分，就唔洗再做卧底咁危險<br />\n名義上又立左功，高層局住要升佢<br />\n呢條友醒到"},{"pid":"04e4594f000ef7d45895ecbb81e1f161bd8977b9","tid":846380,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:32:34.000Z","msg":"戇豆？你就想 你戇九咋 呢個年代仲做老黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b343c49ead0878b7e1b55935125a7b188d260881","tid":846380,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7411b674c805